Package: mfclim
Title: Download Météo-France data using API and SYNOP open data.
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Nicolas", 
           family = "Moiroux", 
           email = "nicolas.moiroux@ird.fr", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6755-6167"))
Description: Download climatological data from the Météo-France public API 'Données climatologiques' and SYNOP open data archives. It provides functions to authenticate, list stations, retrieve station metadata, request climate data, download files, and import data directly into R.
